            "title": "POLÍTICA DE TROCA E DEVOLUÇÃO",
            "content": {
              "content": "<div style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><div style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><section id=\"institucional\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><div style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">POLÍTICA DE TROCA E DEVOLUÇÃO</span></strong></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Considerações Iniciais</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Nossa missão é oferecer aos clientes da Hospitalar Distribuidora apenas produtos de alta qualidade, tudo isso através dos melhores fornecedores do mercado. Ao enviar os produtos, mantemos seu estado original em que o recebemos do fabricante, portanto, caso aconteça alguma eventualidade, informe-se através da seguinte política de troca e devolução baseada no Código de Defesa do Consumidor. </span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Troca e Devolução</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Ambas ações devem ser realizadas em até 07 (sete) dias consecutivos após o recebimento do produto. Se ele apresentar algum defeito ou se estiver insatisfeito com a compra, comunique o Setor de Atendimento ao Cliente (SAC) para assim solicitar a devolução ou troca. </span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Prazo para Troca</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Temos 30 (trinta) dias de prazo para analisar se sua solicitação preenche os requisitos de nossa Política de Troca e Devolução, a contar a partir da data que recebeu o produto. Caso preencha, enviaremos outro produto como solicitado. </span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Condições do Produto</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">A realização da troca/devolução do produto deve ser realizada pelo consumidor através da seguinte forma:</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">1 - Encaminhe o produto sem indícios de uso, com a embalagem original intacta; sem violações no lacre do fabricante;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">2 - A Nota Fiscal Eletrônica, o manual e todos os acessórios do produto devem ser encaminhados juntamente com o mesmo.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Não serão realizadas trocas/devoluções caso a Hospitalar Distribuidora observar indícios de mau uso, falta da etiqueta de lote, ausência da Nota Fiscal ou inexistência de defeitos (em casos de troca).</span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Garantia do Produto</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Ao observar defeito no produto adquirido no prazo de 07 (sete) dias consecutivos após a entrega do mesmo, o consumidor deve entrar em contato com a Hospitalar Distribuidora. </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Caso o consumidor observe defeitos no produto depois do prazo de 07 (sete) dias consecutivos após a entrega do mesmo, ele deverá entrar em contato com o fabricante para obter instruções sobre esclarecimento ou assistências técnicas disponíveis credenciadas por ele, indicadas no menu, para resolução do problema. </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Nós, da Hospitalar Distribuidora, estamos à total disposição para ajudar o consumidor caso ele apresente dificuldades em encontrar o contato do fabricante ou assistência técnica. Também auxiliamos caso não solucionarem o problema no prazo legal.</span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Direito de Arrependimento </span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Se o prazo de 7 (sete) dias consecutivos após o recebimento do produto coincidir com uma data em que não expediente na Hospitalar Distribuidora, a desistência se prorroga para o 1º dia útil subsequente. Desistências devem ser comunicadas ao Setor de Atendimento ao Consumidor (SAC).</span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Restituição de Valores</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">A restituição do pagamento será feita pela Hospitalar Distribuidora da mesma forma de pagamento escolhida na hora da compra, e será realizada após o recebimento e análise do produto. </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">A Hospitalar Distribuidora compromete-se a solicitar o cancelamento de transações pagas através do cartão de crédito no prazo de 03 (três) dias úteis, caso o cliente solicitar. O estorno acontecerá na fatura seguinte ou na próxima de uma só vez, independente do número de parcelas selecionadas na compra. O prazo do ressarcimento é exclusivamente dependente da administradora do cartão. </span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Caso a compra tenha sido realizada via boleto bancário ou débito em conta, a restituição é realizada num prazo de até 10 (dez) dias úteis por meio de depósito bancário na conta corrente do consumidor. Caso ele não possua conta corrente, a Hospitalar Distribuidora fará uma ordem de pagamento em nome do consumidor, podendo ser resgatada nas agências do Banco do Brasil, basta que ele apresente documento de identidade e CPF. </span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Cancelamento ou Desistência de Compra que está com a Transportadora</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Caso desistir da compra após a emissão da nota fiscal, recuse a entrega do produto adquirido. Assim que o produto retornar à sede da Hospitalar Distribuidora, será realizada a restituição do valor pago através da mesma forma de pagamento selecionada na hora da compra. </span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Recusa de Produto</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Recuse o recebimento do produto e informe a Hospitalar Distribuidora através do Serviço de Atendimento ao Consumidor (SAC) caso ocorra:</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">1 - Embalagem avariada ou aberta;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(8