 initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">4 - Ausência de acessórios</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\">Se o comprador ainda aceitar o produto, mesmo ele nas condições citadas acima, ele deve entrar em contato com a SAC em até 72 horas. </span></p><p style=\"list-style-type: none;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><br data-mce-bogus=\"1\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style: none; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(88, 89, 91); outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; outline-color: initial; outline-width: initial;\" data-mce-style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: Arial; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0,